Innovative Public and Private Sector Education
Leading Provider of Counsel and Training for People Management, Behavioral Science, Ethics, and Emotional Growth in Law Enforcement and Human Resources

Our mission is to contribute to the success of any public or private sector organization. We believe that any organization’s strength is their people and to get the most from those people’s strengths and talents you can implement ethical training that utilizes both pragmatism as well as empathy. Employee buy-in is crucial to the success of this training. Critical thinking is a key to a successful transformation and is the basis of our seminars. In our eyes, professionalism and excellence is defined on the basis of objective judgment, integrity, loyalty, dedication, honesty and respect, but most importantly, the ability to exhibit emotionally intelligent behaviors under the most stressful and unimaginable conditions.

We offer a series of behavioral and ethical training seminars that you can use to establish a standard in your department or organization. Establishing a baseline for your organization

● Increasing employee buy-in and improving morale and productivity

name: Landmark Construction (Loomis)
hq: 5948 King Road, Loomis, CA, 95650, United States
overview:
Landmark Construction was established to create a new model for collaboratively building inspiring public facilities.

The concept for Landmark Construction came to light during a casual barbeque among neighbors. Lamenting the arguments, dissension and frustration that typically accompanied major public construction projects, Landmark founders Joe Bittaker and Paul Hanson agreed that there had to be a better way.

They resolved to establish a new way of doing business that resulted in public sector clients benefiting from methods that are often used in private projects, built on the foundation of collaboration.

With proactive planning, Joe and Paul forged better ways to work with architects, owners and subcontractors. By working together early in the process, they uncovered problems and opportunities, and made changes to improve projects long before the first foundation was poured. The partners instilled a company-wide philosophy of customer service and a dedication to working in partnership to find the best solutions at every phase of planning and construction.

Through honest assessment of project goals and practical recommendations to improve constructability, Joe and Paul successfully resolved unexpected problems and met difficult budget and time constraints. Landmark’s cooperative approach delighted owners and built a reputation that attracted other clients. As a result, Landmark has completed hundreds of millions of dollars of complex projects with an unmatched record of delivering 100% of projects on time, within budget and without dispute. The passion for collaboration burns brightly through Landmark’s entire operation. And they still like to barbeque when celebrating the completion of a project.
specialites: Construction Management, Modernizations, Lease-Leaseback, Renovations, Pre-Construction Services, Collaboration, Design-Build, Educational Facilities, Public Facilities, Athletic Facilities and Fields

name: VasDeBlock medical ApS
hq: Storkevaenget 8, Karise, DK-4653, Denmark
overview:
Using hormonal contraceptives is not acceptable for many women, and many men ask for alternative contraception methods. VasDeBlock have developed a medical device as contraception for men. 
Current male sterilisation is surgical and difficult to reverse/undo, so there is a need for non-surgical, easily reversible male sterilization method. VasDeBlock can offer an alternative to vasectomy and hormonal contraception. 
Medical device placement via a thin catheter through an endoscope, without surgery.
The great benefits is fast and simple placement and removal procedure and economically attractive to patient and doctors. 
Devices are inserted through urethra and into the vas deferens. The devices block the vas deferens and prevents the passage of spermatozoa. The male is then sterilized for shorter or longer.
If the procedure needs to be undone, the devices are endoscopically withdrawn, with e.g. a snare or basket.
The procedure has been discussed with, and accepted by KOL urologists and MD´s.
Primary target group is couples wishing surgical birth control, men in relationships who are considering vasectomy and men who wants temporary sterilization.
B2B group is privately practicing urologist performing vasectomy procedures today.
Right now VasDeBlock is looking for investments. Please contact us for more information.
specialites: Medico, Medical devices, Sterilization and vasectomy, R&D

Но можно ли узнать, как «работает» наш потребитель? Узнать и понять – изнутри, досконально, так, как мы знаем своё дело? Здесь и сейчас Вы можете найти ответ. И этот ответ – «да». Добро пожаловать в Neurotrend!
Лаборатория Neurotrend занимается нейромаркетинговыми исследованиями. Мы используем собственную студию-комплекс, работа в котором основана на трекинге глаз, электроэнцефалограмме, кожно-гальванической реакции, кардиограмме и ряде других физиологических показателей. Полученные данные позволяют понять, на что смотрел потребитель, что именно он видел и что чувствовал. Инструментарий исследований позволяет отследить первопричину мотивации потребителя, которая порой фиксируется только подсознанием – и нашей аппаратурой. Тот, кто контролирует реакцию потребителя, сможет создать уникальные продающие инструменты.
Neurotrend – это современная исследовательская лаборатория. Благодаря созданному инструментарию область применения наших исследований ограничена только вашими желаниями – начиная от рекламы и кинопроизводства и заканчивая строительными бизнесом и военным производством.
specialites: Нейромаркетинговые исследования

hq: Hultschiner Straße 8, München, 81677, Germany
overview:
Das einzigartige Angebot von Süddeutscher Verlag Veranstaltungen erstreckt sich von großen Fachkongressen, Konferenzen und Tagungen über Seminare und Expertenvorträge bis zu Empfängen und Golfturnieren. Mit jährlich mehreren zehntausend Teilnehmern werden aktuelle Themen herausragender Referenten u.a. aus Politik, Wirtschaft, Wissenschaft und Forschung beleuchtet. 

Anspruchsvolle Fachausstellungen, Firmenpräsentationen und Besichtigungen begleiten die Fachveranstaltungen. Der „AUTOMOBIL-ELEKTRONIK-Kongress“, der „Deutsche Energiekongress“, der „Deutsche Maschinenbau-Gipfel“ und die „Münchner AIDS- und Hepatitis-Tage” sowie viele andere sind im Markt als renommierte Veranstaltungen bekannt. Darüber hinaus plant und organisiert der Süddeutsche Verlag Veranstaltungen auf den jeweiligen Kundenwunsch zugeschnittene Veranstaltungsformate auch als Dienstleistung. 

Veranstaltungen der Süddeutschen Zeitung
Süddeutsche Zeitung Events organisiert alle Veranstaltungen, die unter dem Namen „Süddeutsche Zeitung“ durchgeführt werden. Die Veranstaltungen, ihre Themenvielfalt und die Auswahl der Gäste aus Politik, Wirtschaft und Wissenschaft sind herausragend und stets durch die Nähe zur Süddeutschen Zeitung geprägt. Das Veranstaltungsprogramm reicht von spannenden Diskussionsrunden mit Wirtschaftsexperten und Politikern, über anspruchsvolle Expertenvorträge aus Wissenschaft und Forschung bis hin zur erlebnisreichen Lesenacht, der „Nacht der Autoren“. 

Golfveranstaltungen
Der Süddeutsche Zeitung Business Golf Cup bietet erfolgreichen Managern und Firmenteams die Möglichkeit, auf den schönsten Golfplätzen Deutschlands Ball- und Businesskontakte zu pflegen, neue Geschäftsbeziehungen aufzubauen und sich für die Finalreisen zu qualifizieren. Die Abteilung Süddeutsche Zeitung Golf ist verantwortlich für die Konzeption, Organisation und persönliche Betreuung der beliebten Turnierserie der Süddeutschen Zeitung.
specialites: Konferenzen, Kongresse, Seminare, Tagungen, Events, Inhouse-Schulungen, Golf-Events, Workshops

name: Broadcasting Standards Authority
overview:
The BSA was set up under the Broadcasting Act 1989(external) to oversee the broadcasting standards regime in New Zealand. We do this by deciding complaints that broadcasts have breached standards, by doing research, and also by providing information about broadcasting standards. 

We come under the umbrella of the Ministry for Culture and Heritage, and our Minister is the Minister of Broadcasting, the Hon Amy Adams(external). However, we are an Independent Crown Entity, which means, among other things, that the government cannot direct us in our work.

The Authority board consists of four members who make the decisions about complaints and who govern the BSA itself. We have a small staff who provide support to the members and who run the day-to-day office services.

We are essentially an appeal body, which is why complaints generally go to the broadcaster first (with the exception of privacy issues and election advertisements). Our decisions can be appealed to the High Court.

name: The Tax Sniper
hq: 2124 Cannes Drive, Carrollton, TX, 75006, United States
overview:
Tax preparation - gathering all your receipts and documents in January and filling in the right boxes on the right forms by April 15 - is hardly the optimal way of protecting your assets. At The Tax Sniper we are committed to tax planning, and to coaching you through the year on how to best take advantage of tax laws in a proactive manner to protect your wealth. Too often we only think in offensive term about how to grow our wealth - what will we do to bring more money in. But part of our overall strategy has to include defense, and a huge part of defending what we have worked so hard for, is to minimize our tax liability and keep what we have earned, in our pockets. 
A CPA can only memorialize what you present her with. But we help you take a more proactive stance in understanding what to do at each step of the way so that when it actually comes time to prepare your taxes, you're already in the best shape possible.

name: epinamics GmbH
hq: Wachtelstr. 15, Berlin, 14195, Germany
overview:
epinamics is a Berlin-based, privately owned research and development company, focusing on an innovative drug delivery technology for dermal and transdermal applications of cosmetic, pharmaceutical and veterinary products. 

Based on the unique polymer-based and film-forming technology, called Liqui-Patch, epinamics is developing a portfolio of own products where (active) pharmaceutical ingredients are administered in liquid formulations. The almost invisible Liqui-Patch is flexible in respect to its scope of application, administration, dosage and skin adherence. 

The platform technology was originally invented by scientists at Intendis GmbH and the Saarland University and is covered by well-differentiated issued patents for a broad range of pharmaceutical ingredients. 

Liqui-Patch is a technology form from which various medicinal products can emerge with low cost of goods.
 
epinamics is offering its pharmaceutical research and development expertise to support your company in getting innovative technology products to market quickly. Whether you require an existing product in our technology range or want our support in developing your pharmaceutical ingredients as innovative dermal or transdermal products, we have the capabilities to get your medical products to the retail shelves fast.
specialites: Dermal & Transdermal Pharmaceutical Products, Self-Medication Products, Research & Development, Supergenerics, Metered Dose Applications, Innovative Medicine

name: Dick van Aken Architectuur
hq: Groen van Prinstererstraat 38, Arnhem, Gelderland, 6828 VX, Netherlands
overview:
Passie en een persoonlijke benadering. Poëzie met 2 voeten op de grond. Daar sta ik voor!
Bent u op zoek naar een VERRASSEND, RUIMTELIJK EN DUURZAAM ontwerp voor NIEUWBOUW of VERBOUW, of bent u op zoek naar hulp bij HERBESTEMMING van een LEEGSTAAND gebouw of gebouwen? Ik kan u helpen!

Ik wil mensen verblijden met ruimtelijke ideeën. Ontwerpen is voor mij een zoektocht naar een verrassende wending in het alledaagse. Ruimtes wil ik tot de verbeelding laten spreken en boven het functionele laten uitstijgen. Daarin streef ik naar een intensiteit van sfeer, heldere eenvoud, bijzondere ruimtelijkheid en lichtinval.

In het proces van ontwerp tot en met realisatie werk ik vanuit een betrokken creatieve samenwerking met opdrachtgevers, gebruikers, adviseurs en bouwers.

Meer dan ooit gaat het om het creëren van blijvende waarden voor de beleving, omgeving, duurzaamheid en economie. Ik ontwerp duurzaam en voor de toekomst. Goed bruikbare gebouwen met hedendaagse kennis en technieken, met passie voor het ambacht en historisch besef. Duurzaamheidprincipes worden op een innovatieve manier in gebouwen geïntegreerd. In het ontwerpproces wordt alle kennis gecombineerd, tot een gebouw waarin alles klopt. 

Mijn specialisme is nieuwbouw en verbouw van particuliere woningen en collectief opdrachtgeverschap, herbestemmingsopgaven voor monumentale gebouwen en bedrijfsmatigegebouwen.
Daarnaast heb ik ervaring met sportgebouwen, woongebouwen, een woontoren, een woonzorgcentrum en diverse eerste-lijns gezondheidscentra en praktijkruimtes. 

VAARDIGHEDEN VAN CONCEPT TOT MAKEN:
- Architectuur - Stedenbouw - Interieur
- Tekenwerkzaamheden in alle fasen van het ontwerpproces
- Bouwregelgeving en omgevingsvergunning 
- Haalbaarheidsstudies, Inventarisatieonderzoeken, Ideeënstudies, Conceptontwikkeling. 
- Werken in ontwerpteams, bouwteams, gebruikersgroepen
- Duurzaamheid
- Prijs- en contractvorming en bouwbegeleiding
specialites: architectuur, herbestemmen, stedenbouw, nieuwbouw, verbouw

name: ACADI - Association des cadres et dirigeants pour le progrès social et économique
hq: 32 rue du Mont Thabor, Paris, 75001, France
overview:
L’Acadi est une association de cadres et de dirigeants qui partagent des valeurs de progrès social et économique, au service de l’intérêt général. L’Acadi est politiquement et financièrement indépendante.
C’est un lieu d’échanges et de débats entre les secteurs de l’économie, entre les générations.

L’Acadi est active à Paris et à Lyon. En sa qualité d’association, l’Acadi adhère à l’Institut de l’Entreprise.

L’Acadi a été créée en 1946, à la Libération.
Les trente premières années – les Trente Glorieuses – ont connu une croissance extraordinaire du niveau de vie et de la consommation. Avec les trente années suivantes, les crises de l’énergie, les délocalisations en cascade, la croissance vertigineuse des endettements publics et une financiarisation non maîtrisée de l’économie, ont créé ou aggravé des déséquilibres de tous ordres.

L’Acadi donne la parole à celles et ceux qui, par leurs initiatives et leur créativité, contribuent à un développement responsable et durable ; sur des thèmes comme :
 > la mondialisation des activités
 > l’économie financière,
 > la technologie et les innovations
 > la responsabilité sur l’environnement
 > les business models en ‘’disruption’’
 > les modes de travail et de management
 > la protection sociale, les inégalités

Adhérer à l’Acadi, c’est participer aux transformations des entreprises et de la société, avec le projet de répondre aux aspirations légitimes des collaborateurs ou des citoyens.

name: Sabin.io
overview:
Sabin.io is a Data Engineering practice. Our focus is on helping companies deliver data systems. We help companies build sustainable applications that consider the support and ongoing development. The use of agile methodologies is fantastic but needs to be aligned with the engineering practices of testing, continuous integration/delivery and a feedback loop to enable continual improvement.

Our experience stretches from windows server management and automation through to the support and management of BI systems. We have strong application development experience which means we are able to deliver and support solutions that work with all those involved in application development from .net developers though to DBAs. We are proud to break down the historical boundaries that often exist between development, infrastructure and DBAs, working with all groups, educating allaying fears and to deliver complete solutions. 

We are a company with a great depth of knowledge. We have the first SQL Server MCM, have a very strong relationship with SQL Server product team and the world wide SQL Server community. In the unlikely event we don’t know the answer, we are very confident we are able to find the answer to your questions. Whilst you may only have one person on site, you can be assured that they can draw on the knowledge of all those in Sabin.io.

Our unrivalled SQL Server experience means we have worked on many applications where performance is believed to be at the peak of capability and been able to greatly improve it. Optimising websites from five second response times to milliseconds and transforming multi hour batch processes that process millions of rows and block all write activity into friendly transactionally consistent batch processes.

There are two distinct types of fund – Villa Funds and Apartment Funds – both following the same formula of sharing the equity ownership and running costs of the properties.
 
Instead of spending a very large sum buying a wholly-owned property at a single destination, subscribers invest a much smaller amount in a portfolio of splendid fully-staffed villas with private pools in different countries, cultures and climate zones. Or they can choose to invest in a collection of magnificent apartments in the most exciting cities of either Europe or North America, or in a portfolio of apartments in the single destinations of London and New York.

name: BestComm Networks, Inc

overview:
In business since 1994, BestComm is not only an exclusive certified dealer of Mitel Systems, but also the endorsed vendor of the world’s largest hotel chain, Best Western. Staffed by a team of certified technicians, who have an intimate understanding of the importance of ‘guest satisfaction,’ BestComm specializes in the design, implementation, integration and support of PBX, voice mail, call accounting, internet, local area network and security systems.

With more than 2,500 systems installed from Alaska to the Caribbean and from Newfoundland to Hawaii, BestComm provides state-of-the-art IP-based PBX systems and cost-effective business class high-speed internet systems to hotels - both national brands and independents.
 
We also design and implement various enterprise applications, including VoIP, call centers, local area networks, multi-site voice & data networks, and mobility solutions for dynamic enterprise environments.

BestComm offers a wide range of services including local area network support, remote maintenance and troubleshooting services, hardware replacement support, 24/7 guest support, home page redirect services and e-mail relay with anti-virus and spam control services.

BestComm’s wide array of internet solutions is designed to accommodate any building infrastructure from pre-existing telephone wiring to a fiber optic cable plant. Our Network Engineers have the experience and resources to design and implement a local area network or high-speed internet access system in virtually any building infrastructure. Let BestComm design the best suited network for your business needs whether utilizing wireless, fiber or pre-existing telephone wiring.

BestComm has expanded to include state-of-the-art Surveillance/Security Systems, which can be customized to accommodate each and every business’ particular needs. From motion-activated infrared high definition cameras to multi-channel networked DVR's to remote system access & control.

name: Lavandería Malagueña
overview:
Servicios integrales de lavandería • Higiene y desinfección total.

Empresa pionera e innovadora en Málaga en el sector de la lavandería industrial,
ponemos a su disposición todos nuestros años de experiencia en la innovación y optimización de procesos, con el convencimiento de poder mejorar sus costes globales y el servicio a sus clientes.

Como empresa certificada por el Instituto Técnico Español de Limpieza (ITEL), apostamos por la Calidad, la Higiene y la preservación del Medio ambiente.

Hemos desarrollado nuevos procesos de lavado de prendas con los que conseguimos una desinfección total (virus, bacterias, parásitos, hongos,...). Cuando el textil es procesado de acuerdo con nuestros estándares de calidad, el resultado es una prenda desodorizada, hipo-alergénica y con niveles de pH neutro.

Además de notar mayor blancura y limpieza, con nuestro servicio de lavandería podrán duplicar la vida útil de las prendas. Lo que supondrá un beneficio económico para su establecimiento.

El servicio de Lavandería consiste en recoger la ropa en las instalaciones del cliente, procesarla y devolverla en perfectas condiciones para su uso en un plazo establecido previamente.

Con el Renting (alquiler de prendas) ponemos a disposición del cliente las dotaciones necesarias de ropa de cama, felpa y mantelería. Nos hacemos cargo de la adquisición de la ropa de habitaciones y mantelería asesorando al cliente sobre el cálculo de las dotaciones y calidades que mejor se adapten a sus necesidades.

Trabajamos con proveedores de máximo nivel y calidad. Aseguramos el mantenimiento del stock pactado inicialmente con reposiciones anuales.

Se puede personalizar tanto en ropa de cama (sábanas, fundas de almohada,…), como felpa (toallas) o mantelería. Así, nuestros clientes pueden utilizar su diseño corporativo (logos, colores, estilos…).

name: Redemption Games, Inc.
hq: Palomar Airport Road, Carlsbad, ca, 92011, United States
overview:
Redemption Games, Inc. was started in the Summer of 2015 by Michael Witz and Dan Lin, two friends who have had a long history of starting companies and building products that millions of people love. 
 
The mobile games business has become one of the most competitive industries the world has ever seen. There are hundreds of thousands of games in the app store and to be able to rise to the top requires a unique combination of skill and effort, from how the game is designed to how its marketed and operated as a live service. There are no silver bullets and no shortcuts.
 
Over the last several years in the trenches of free to play game development, we’ve evolved our own unique approach to building games that we are excited to unleash. First and foremost, our “playbook for making games” starts with bringing together the right people. In a highly competitive market for talent, we are grateful and excited to begin this new endeavor with an amazing founding team of developers, including key talent from SGN Games, Zynga, Google, Amazon and Rockstar. 

To top it all off, we get to do this with an amazing publishing partner and investor, Scopely, who we believe has built the most extensive and effective marketing platform in the entire mobile industry. Scopely brings both a stacked deck of their own game development talent to the table and the strength of a strong financial partner, ensuring once we build a hit game, we will be able to fully realize its potential. 
 
If you’d like to join a small, elite group of developers looking to create an outstanding new mobile game, then please get in touch. jobs@redemptiongames.com
specialites: mobile games

name: EFIM (Expert&finance Investment Managers)
hq: 18 Place de la Madeleine, Paris, 75008, France
overview:
Efim (Expert et finance Investment Managers) est la société de gestion filiale d’Expert&finance.
Elle a obtenu son agrément AMF le 22 août 2014 sous le numéro GP 14000036.
 
Sa philosophie s’inscrit dans une approche patrimoniale de la gestion. Son objectif principal est la recherche constante de performance, en contrepartie d’un risque de perte en capital limité dans les grandes phases de baisse des marchés.
 
Toute notre gestion est mise en œuvre via la multigestion.
Notre process allie l’analyse des économies, des marchés, la sélection des fonds et la gestion du risque.
 
Pour cette gestion du risque Efim travaille avec Active Asset Allocation , société indépendante d’ingénierie financière composée d’experts en gestion d’actifs, actuariat et recherche académique, dont les modèles propriétaires permettent de valider la compatibilité des allocations définies avec un niveau de perte maximum préalablement déterminé.

Efim est gérant financier par délégation de Generali Investments Luxembourg S.A. pour les fonds Efim Alpha et Efim Sigma.

name: ForceChange
overview:
Who We Are

The Force Change community is comprised of passionate individuals who care deeply about issues such as animal rights, the environment, human rights, social justice, progressive politics, and more. We are writers, students, professionals, activists and citizens. We aim to provide the important news, policy and analysis intended to arm people with the information and tools necessary to Force Change in the unsustainable status quo. Learn more about us here.

What We Do

We are concerned that our health and resources are being threatened by government neglect and corporate malfeasance.We are frustrated with our leaders in both the public and private sectors who are not taking the necessary steps to alter this untenable course. We aim to promote discussion, analysis and ultimately change regarding the most pressing issues facing our society today.

How You Can Help

Please help us force change by signing and sharing our petitions and joining in the discussion with your comments. There is, of course, no need to agree with the authors of any petitions or other commenters, but please be constructive and respectful.

How Big Are We?

Our newsletters go out to over half a million citizen activists, creating a giant wave for positive change. Every month, over four million pages are viewed by ForceChange Network community members.

name: Agape Inventory Donation
overview:
Agape Inventory Donation accepts new corporate product donations that can be utilized by our network of 501(c)3 nonprofit organizations serving children, and the ill and needy. We also accept donations of a monetary variety from individuals to aid the cover cost of shipping as well as distribution of product donations to the nonprofits that need them most. Our efforts save money, reduce waste, increase non-profit effectiveness, and stimulate business.

WHY SHOULD YOUR COMPANY DONATE INVENTORY TO AGAPE INVENTORY DONATION?
Sometimes companies produce excess, orders are cancelled or particular models are discontinued. Any merchandise this isn't sold adds up, takes up valuable warehouse room and costs a great deal to store.

To make room for newer brands and products, you can donate your excess merchandise to Agape Inventory Donation. If it is an approved donation, the U.S. Government can give your company a tax deduction and we can give all the excess inventory to schools, churches and non-profits for FREE. Agape Inventory Donation members can utilize these extra tools and supplies to assist teachers in giving better lessons, shelters, for another example, take care of more people and churches are able to provide more help for the needy. This creates a win-win for all involved!

When a donation shipment comes in to Agape Inventory Donation's warehouse in St. Louis, Missouri, the merchandise is sorted through, organized and documented for our website and catalogs. Each month our members receive Agape Inventory Donation's catalogs with a wide variety of items they need to operate their respective organizations. These items range from toys, clothes, books, office supplies, tools, toiletries, DVDs, crafts, and more! All the merchandise is absolutely FREE. Members only pay a small fee to cover the cost of shipping and handling.

Please contact us to donate money, products, or for general inquires -- http://www.agapedonate.org/donate.html
specialites: Inventory Donation, Unused Inventory Donation, Inventory Management, Closeout Inventory, Excess Inventory Donations

overview:
Understanding European technology policy and politics

Decoding Europe informs Silicon Valley corporate comms and public policy professionals about developments in policy-making and politics in Europe, comparing them to similar developments in the United States. name: Solutions Bay Sp. z o.o.
hq: ul. Ostódzka 38, Wrocław, Wrocław, Dolny Śląsk, 54-116, Poland
overview:
Solutions Bay - Zatoka Możliwości - wspieramy managerów i organizacje we wdrażaniu właściwych zmian. 

Stanowimy zespół, w którym każdy członek posiada specjalistyczne ( zarówno teoretyczne jak i praktyczne) doświadczenie w zakresie doradztwa biznesowego. 
Jesteśmy przekonani, że nieustanny rozwój jest głównym czynnikiem sukcesu, zarówno osobistego jak i organizacyjnego.

Zależy nam na maksymalizacji korzyści pochodzących z inwestycji czasu oraz zasobów naszych partnerów, dlatego proponujemy programy dedykowane oraz szkolenia otwarte.

W przypadku programów dedykowanych wszystkie treści są dopasowywane do potrzeb organizacji.

Diagnozowanie obszarów wymagających usprawnienia odbywa się w ścisłej kooperacji.

Nasz zespół rozmawia z przedstawicielami firmy o aktualnej sytuacji organizacji, dokonuje analizy i doboru odpowiednich treści.

Poniższa lista zawiera wyszczególnione obszary w których się specjalizujemy i opracowujemy programy rozwojowe:

1. Komunikacja 
(Jakie są zasady skutecznego porozumiewania się? Jak tworzyć komunikaty by być zrozumianym? W jaki sposób przekazywać informacje?)

2. Motywowanie 
(Co zrobić by wzmocnić skuteczność zespołu? Jak motywować i jak karać pracowników? Jak zachęcać współpracowników do efektywniejszej pracy?)

3. Leadership
(Jak zbudować autorytet i co robić by być dobrym liderem? Jakie są zasady i techniki, zwiększające wpływ lidera na ludzi i organizację?)

4. Zarządzanie zmianą
(Jak przygotować organizację i ludzi do wdrożenia zmiany? Co robić by została ona przyjęta bez oporu? Jakie narzędzia wspierają jej wdrożenie?)

5. Zarządzanie projektami
(Jak zrealizować projekt tak, by zmieścił się w czasie, budżecie oraz posiadał założoną jakość? Jakie techniki i narzędzia w tym pomagają? Jakie błędy są najczęściej popełniane i jakich uniknąć?)

6. Zarządzanie procesami
(Jak planować, modelować, restrukturyzować oraz zarządzać procesami istniejącymi w organizacji? Jakie narzędzia to ułatwiają?)
specialites: zarządzanie projektami, komunikacja, zarządzanie zmianą, motywowanie, leadership, przywództwo, zarządzanie procesami, team bulding/ budowanie zespołów, zarządzanie strategiczne, coaching, public speaking

overview:
QR-Patrol System has been developed by Terracom Informatics LTD to bring a solution in real time monitoring and managing patrolling Security Guards, Lone Workers and Industrial Workers assuring their safety at all times.

QR-Patrol is a Real Time guard monitoring system which skyrockets the efficiency of security companies and offer them the ability to upgrade their services via technology. In brief, QR-Patrol incorporates all the basic features of a smart guard tour system solution:

- Create and connect sites with checkpoints
- Receive SOS alerts and take immediate action
- Get e-mail notifications for missed, early or late passed checkpoints
- Send incidents reports to your clients or to the Monitoring Center
- Manage patrols remotely in real-time
- Verify guard tours online and check missed patrols

QR-Patrol guard tour system relieves officers from daily time-consuming processes such as filling paper reports and making repetitive phone calls to the Monitoring Center, provoking confusion and misunderstandings. The whole procedure is defined by strict guidelines and simple actions to take. Guards and officers can quickly send incidents reports, implement patrols and any other guard service by taking advantage of the last innovations in technology.

Companies and Clients are also informed and engaged in the monitoring process in real-time, keeping remote control on every aspect of guard tour services and reacting immediately to any incidents as required.

name: Finan3
overview:
Cooperativa de serveis impulsada per la Taula d'Entitats del Tercer Sector Social català i les federacions que en formen part, amb l'objectiu d'enfortir les capacitats econòmiques i financeres de les entitats socials a Catalunya.

Finan3 pretén aportar solucions a dos dels principals reptes als quals s'enfronten actualment moltes entitats del Tercer Sector social català. D'una banda, les dificultats per accedir al finançament i, de l'altra, la necessitat de millorar la gestió econòmica i financera per afrontar una situació de recursos sovint molt escassos.

La nostra visió va més enllà d'esdevenir una solució circumstancial, volem construir un instrument, al servei del Tercer Sector Social i des de el Tercer Sector social, que impulsi també la creació de noves fórmules de finançament per a les entitats, i que en un futur, canalitzi l'estalvi solidari cap al finançament de projectes socials.

Cooperativa de servicios impulsada por la Mesa de Entidades del Tercer Sector catalán y las federaciones que la conforman, con el objetivo de fortalecer las capacidades económicas y financieras de las entidades sociales que trabajan en Cataluña.

Finan3 pretende aportar soluciones a dos de los principales retos a los que se enfrentan actualmente las entidades del Tercer Sector social catalán. Por un lado, las dificultades para acceder a la financiación y del otro, la necesidad de mejorar la gestión económica de unos recursos cada vez más escasos.

Nuestra visión va más allá de convertirnos en una solución circumstancial. Queremos construir un instrumento, desde y para el Tercer Sector social, que impulse nuevas fórmulas de financiación para las entidades y que en un futuro, permita canalizar el ahorro solidario hacia la financiación de nuevos proyectos.
specialites: Impuls solidari per al Tercer Sector, Fons Solidari del Tercer Sector Social, Servei d'acompanyament financer

overview:
Cash & Carry que ofrece los siguientes productos de forma física, por distribución y en internet

*Artículos de un solo uso: platos, vasos, cubiertos, envases para alimentos, cajas de pizza …
*Manteles, servilletas, celulosa higiénica

*Artículos para celebraciones.
*Hacemos bolsas impresas y artículos personalizados para su negocio.

LA HISTORIA DE NUESTRO ÉXITO

Comercial Andalucía (Máximo Gavira, S. A.) es una empresa en funcionamiento desde 1986, aunque sus inicios se remontan a la década de los 70. Estamos especializados en suministros para hostelería, comercio, colectividades, profesionales y particulares. Nos situamos en La Línea de la Concepción (Cádiz), donde poseemos un negocio abierto al público profesional en régimen de Cash & Carry, a la vez que realizamos la distribución de nuestros productos por las provincias de Cádiz y Málaga y en Gibraltar.

En 2010 comenzamos la venta por internet, avalados por nuestra amplia experiencia en el sector y los años que llevamos trabajando en contacto directo con el público profesional. El cliente que compre en nuestra tienda online puede tener plena confianza en el buen fin de la transacción que realiza.

En nuestras cómodas instalaciones de 3.500 m2, con fácil acceso y amplio aparcamiento, encontrará 10.000 artículos diferentes orientados a satisfacer todas las necesidades del profesional de la hostelería, restauración, alimentación, ocio, comercio, industria y servicios, así como de todo tipo de colectividades.

Über die Konzeption, Planung und Umsetzung bis hin zur Erfolgskontrolle begleitet USP ihre Kunden in Ganzjahresprogrammen und auf Projektebene kompetent und mit Leidenschaft von A bis Z.

name: Towards A Green Education
hq: Adarsh Vista, Bangalore, Karnataka, 560037, India
overview: Towards A Green Education is an organization that aims to help rural and underprivileged children in schools by providing them with stationery as well as to save paper and reduce its wastage. TAGE collects any recyclable paper from schools and communities, and uses the funds generated from its recycling to buy stationery. However, an important aspect is that it removes the blank pages from old notebooks, so that these aren’t wasted - and uses these to make new notebooks with the help of school students. Over the course of one year, TAGE collected over 2200 kilos of used paper, about 50,000 sheets of blank paper, and made over 350 handmade notebooks. On the 29th of June, with some volunteers, TAGE visited a government school in collaboration with Akshara Foundation, and gave 250 children stationery sets - each of which includes a handmade notebook, a 100-page ruled notebook, a box of 10 pencils, two erasers and a sharpener. TAGE plans to visit several more schools in the future - and aims to scale to a level where we can make a significant difference to the world we live in.

name: Recursos Humanos Confiables
overview:
¿Has jugado ajedrez alguna vez? El ajedrez es un juego en el que el ordenamiento y ejecución de
las mejores estrategias, serán las que determinarán la victoria o pérdida del mismo. Esto también sucede en las empresas colocar de forma adecuada a cada persona en el departamento correcto te permite que brindes un buen servicio. Para ello es muy importante que conozcas las habilidades, capacidades y grado de confiabilidad de cada uno de tus empleados; ya que no todos somos “buenos” para todo. 

Hay quienes tienen habilidades para socializar, por ejemplo, ellos perfectamente pueden desempeñar un puesto de atención al público, porque a ti no te gustaría encontrar a una recepcionista que no te sepa dar informes, ¿verdad? Pero eso no se logra por arte de magia, encontrar a la persona idónea para cada labor requiere de profesionales en la materia.

Realizar pruebas psicométricas y de personalidad de te dan la oportunidad de saber con qué habilidades y deficiencias cuenta cada persona para llevar a cabo una labor determinada. Valorar el coeficiente intelectual de un gerente de ventas, no solo te permitirá ver qué capacidad tiene para calcular rápidamente la cantidad de material que la otra empresa necesita, sino también para valorar que otros servicios le puedes ofrecer como empresa.

Te voy a poner un ejemplo: si en tu empresa se manejan bases de datos de clientes, de proveedores y tienes a un empleado resentido; fácilmente él puede vendérselos a la competencia, o bien si en tu empresa se maneja “la receta secreta” y tu asistente personal tiene acceso a ella, a 
o mejor no hoy ni mañana, pero si no es confiable puede usarla para abrir su propio negocio.

Brindar un servicio de excelencia en la intermediación inmobiliaria o de bienes raíces. Ofrecerles a nuestros clientes ofertantes, una venta eficiente de sus bienes inmuebles, y a nuestros clientes demandantes, el inmueble que necesitan según sus posibilidades económicas.

Ser la empresa más reconocida de Bolivia en el rubro de bienes raíces y de desarrollo inmobiliario, por su eficiencia e integridad en la prestación de sus servicios.

Los valores que se practican en NESA son la responsabilidad, integridad, eficiencia, laboriosidad y la perseverancia. 

Principios
Se quiere generar bienestar social y económico para los clientes que confían en NESA, los empleados y funcionarios que trabajan para ella, los proveedores y profesionales independientes que prestan algún servicio y también para los socios accionistas que aportaron en la empresa.

The Oregon Road Runners Club (ORRC) is a non-profit, volunteer-driven community resource that promotes running and walking for the benefit of all --- for fitness, fun, safety, health, and quality of life in the Portland Oregon metro area. Oregon Road Runners Club is the largest West Coast running club, and one of the top 10 largest club members of Road Runners of America (RRCA) nationally.

Follow us at ORRC.NET, on Facebook and Twitter.

The club hosts 15 annual race events as well as evening trainng sessions. 

The races include: 
January - Y2K 10K and Half Marathon (Forest Grove, Or.)

February - Hagg Lake Mud 25K and 50k (Gaston, Or.) 

March - Champoeg 10K, 20K and 30K (Champoeg Park, Or.)

April - Vernonia Half and Full Marathon (Vernonia and Banks, Or.)

May - Hagg Lake 5K, 10K and 10.3M ( Gaston, Or.); Up the Lazy River 10K (West Linn, Or.) on Memorial Day

June - Summer Solistice Sundowner 5K (Oregon City, Or.)

July - July 4th 5K (Wilsonville, Or.) on July 4th

August - Dual Duel 10K solo, 10M relay (Catlin Gable School, Portland, Or.) Garlic Festival 5K and 10K (North Plains, Or.) 

September - Greenway Trail Trial 10K (Beaverton, Or.) on Labor Day; Best Dam Run 10K (Estacada, Or)
 
October - Blue Lake Run 5K and 10K (Fairview/Troutdale, Or.); Autumn Leaves 50K, 50M (Champoeg Park, Or.) 

November: Turkey Trot at the Zoo (Metro Zoo) on Thanksgiving Day 

The evening training sessions are on Tuesdays 6:00 p.m. at Cedar Hills Recreation Center, Beaverton, March thru October, and on Thursdays 6 p.m. at Cleveland High School February thru mid-December.

L’Agenzia di consulenza Albania-Impresa con sedi nelle maggiori città albanesi Tirana, Valona e Lezhe nasce dalla partnership di un gruppo di imprenditori, professionisti Italiani e albanesi, strutturati al fine di garantire all’Imprenditore intenzionato a sviluppare in Albania dei servizi come la delocalizzazione della propria attività produttiva, alla ricerca di nuovi profili commerciali o industriali, a tessere rapporti e relazioni economiche con realtà produttive di tutta l’Area Balcanica. 

La mission che si prefigge la nostra agenzia, è di fornire un servizio serio, efficace ed affidabile all’Imprenditore italiano in cerca di riferimenti nel mercato albanese. L’operatore italiano optando per la nostra Agenzia sceglie di riporre la propria fiducia in una solida realtà composta da professionisti accreditati, piuttosto che affidarsi alla “improvvisazione” ed alla superficialità imperanti nel campo della realizzazione di attività produttive all’estero.

Un pool di Imprenditori, Avvocati, Financial auditors, Consulenti del Lavoro ed aziendali, Notai, sia Italiani che albanesi, tutti di comprovata esperienza, potranno consigliare, assistere, seguire ed indirizzare l’Imprenditore sia nella fase iniziale della propria attività, provvedendo ad ogni incombenza, anche di natura legale e fiscale, necessaria per la costituzione di una Società in Albania e l’avvio della relativa impresa, sia nella fase di vera e propria attività, fornendo assistenza legale e tributaria. Tale assistenza potrà essere fornita all’imprenditore che vorrà avvalersi solo di servizi momentanei, quindi circoscritti ad un solo evento come l’organizzazione di una fiera, il tutto verrà sempre svolto più con tutto il sostegno necessario per operare con serenità e soddisfazione. Da noi ogni rapporto viene costruito su misura, in base alle personali esigenze del cliente, in una logica di produzione di concreta risoluzione dei problemi, di ricerca della qualità totale.

overview: Stichting Meldpunt Modelfotografie is een meldpunt dat (gratis) adviezen geeft aan modellen, (amateur) fotografen, stylisten, Make-Up Artists en modellenbureau’s en deze eventueel doorverwijst wanneer er misstanden binnen de branche worden gemeld. Alle deelnemers zijn vrijwillig actief binnen het meldpunt en ontvangen hiervoor geen vergoeding. De deelnemers van het meldpunt kunnen tevens als getuige-deskundige/branche deskundige optreden binnen juridische procedures of bij mediation. Vanwege de groei van meldingen bij het meldpunt op internet wil deze een stap naar professionalisering zetten door zich daadwerkelijk te vestigen als rechtspersoon. Hierdoor kan het meldpunt meer betekenen bij het verwerken, adviseren, doorverwijzen, etc. van de gemelde of zelf geconstateerde misstanden. Alle deelnemers zullen een participatie overeenkomst tekenen en zich daardoor als vrijwilliger officieel verbinden aan het meldpunt. Binnen deze participatie overeenkomst is een integriteits-, geheimhoudings en exoneratiebeding (aansprakelijkheid) opgenomen. Naast deze overeenkomst is er een gedragscode en meldingsprotocol opgesteld zodat alle activiteiten in het kader van transparatie plaatsvindt.\r\n \r\nDe meldingen van misstanden die veelvuldig binnenkomen bij het meldpunt hebben te maken met: intimidatie (in woord en/of geschrift), niet leveren van foto’s, auteurs- en/of portretrechtelijke zaken, sexuele voorstellen/intimidatie, wanbetaling, spook cq. onterechte facturen (met daarbij intimidatie in woord en/of geschrift dmv onterechte dreiging incassobureau en/of deurwaarder en/of rechtbank wanneer er niet betaald wordt), etc.

name: Merel's Little Big Things
overview:
Uniek beschilderde schatkisten om herinneringen in te bewaren/koesteren voor belangrijke gebeurtenissen in het leven! Uniek cadeau om te krijgen en geven.

Herinneringen om te koesteren voor verschillende gebeurtenissen. Een schatkist.......

bij een geboorte: Met bijvoorbeeld het eerste mutsje, speentje, kleertjes, papieren over de bevalling, kaartjes, consultatieburo boekje e.d.

bij een geboorte/algemeen: Afhankelijk van het formaat kan je er ook voor kiezen om de schatkist te blijven vullen, denk aan een knutselwerkjes, kinderopvangboekje, schoolschriftje, zwemdiploma’s ofwel de periode van kind zijn. Leuk om ook later als cadeau te geven aan je kind.

bij een adoptie: Met spulletjes die uit het land van adoptie komen, de papieren, de kleren bij aankomst e.d.

bij het trouwen: Met bijvoorbeeld het trouwboekje, gastenboek, bruidsbloem, gekregen kaartjes e.d. Ook kan de schatkist een gastenboek zijn. De deksel bijvoorbeeld geschilderd met als inspiratie de uitnodiging. De zijkanten kunnen gebruikt worden voor de namen van de gasten die ze er met speciale acrylsitften op kunnen schrijven of met bijvoorbeeld vingerafdrukken. De kist kan daarna nog afgelakt worden.

ter nagedachtenis: De herinneringen aan de dierbare mensen in ons leven zijn er om te koesteren. Een mooie schatkist met deze schatten aan herinneringen kan helpen bij het verwerken in deze verdrietige periode.

het opbergen van speelgoed/hobby spullen: Geschilderd naar wens, bijvoorbeeld geinspireerd op kinderkamer/geboortekaartje of als een meubelstuk passend in de woonkamer.

als cadeau, bijvoorbeeld voor de kraamtijd, een babyshower, bij een jubileum, huwelijkscadeau, afscheid van een collega, emigreren, of een 'doorgeefschatkist' voor vrienden, waarbij eenieder steeds iets toevoegt, ook voor therapeutische hulp aan kinderen en volwassenen kan een schatkist een waardevol hulpmiddel zijn.

Tevens kan je voor een muurschildering terecht bij Merel's Little Big Things.
specialites: herinneringsschatkisten, muurschilderingen, persoonlijk cadeau

name: Black(s) to the Future
hq: France
overview:
www.blackstothefuture.com

Black(s) to the Future est une plateforme transmedia, nourrie d'afrofuturisme, (pro-)posant un regard moderne - durable et décomplexé - sur l'africanité et ses modes d'expression.

Nos objectifs ?

 • DÉPASSER un inconscient collectif stéréotypé sur l’Afrique et sa diaspora ;
 • FOURNIR une pensée critique et référencée sur ce qu’est l’africanité ;
 • NOURRIR l’inspiration à travers une vision afrofuturiste du monde.

A la fois médium et média, B(s)ttF s’articule selon deux logiques, la première visant la diffusion de pratiques et de savoirs, l’autre - plus pragmatique - de création de valeur. Nous regroupons pour l'heure un mook (magazine/book) et des mixtapes en ligne, puis à venir, des vidéos (fiction, art, reportages), un studio de création graphique et une marque.

Arts, philosophie, entrepreneuriat, mode & design, écologie... L’africanité est un fait qui traverse tout – époques, nationalités, intérêts. Nous voulons lui rendre la dignité qu’elle mérite.

__________

Black(s) to the Future fonctionne sur le modèle d'un collectif à géométrie variable, avec pour capitaine à bord Mawena Yehouessi. Nous sommes tous - pour l'instant - bénévoles. Ensemble, nous souhaitons mettre en avant de nouvelles approches (en termes de fond et de forme), non seulement de ce que sont/seraient les cultures noires et leurs relations avec l’Afrique, mais quant à leurs dimensions prospectives.

Black(s) to the Future se veut donc un espace d’interaction et de rapprochement d’initiatives créatives, relevant le défi AFRO + FUTUR : artistes, chercheu.r/se.s ou simples curieu.x/ses… Il s’adresse aux acteurs et actrices du monde de demain!
specialites: Afrofuturisme, Arts / Recherche / Prospective, Evénementiel

name: Car Free Vancouver Society
overview:
In 2005, the Commercial Drive Festival launched the first community- driven Car-Free Festival in Vancouver as a response to the provincial government’s Gateway Program, also known as the Port Mann/Highway 1 Improvement Project. Organizers also wanted to create a community festival at a time when there were few such events in the city. The Festival was wholly volunteer-organized and presented, involving over 30 core organizers and 300 volunteers. It was an enormous success, bringing over 25,000 people out to celebrate the community and party in the street.

After that, the Festival happened in 2006 and twice in the summer of 2007, snowballing in popularity and attracting up to 40,000 people per day. Clearly, car-free days were an idea whose time had come.

The first annual Car-Free Vancouver Day, on Sunday June 15, 2008 ushered in the next phase in this bold experiment that had been gradually happening in Vancouver for many years. It took the car-free meme to the whole city, and represented the next level in our evolution toward healthy communities, authentic cultural celebrations, and car-free streets. On that day, FOUR communities presented their own Car-Free Festivals: Kitsilano, West End, Main Street, and Commercial Drive. Each Festival was envisioned and organized by the local core organizers, and each had a unique flavour.

We are doing it again this year! And we're expanding to North Vancouver with a new (returning!) festival on Saturday, August 22nd.

name: Cahir House Hotel
hq: The Square, Cahir, Tipperary, Ireland
overview: A truly magical residence that blends the warmth of a Historical Town House with the style of a contemporary Irish hotel, Cahir House Hotel is the leading 3 star hotel in Cahir, County Tipperary. Inside, the warmth of the blazing fire, is matched by the warmth of the welcome. This former manor house offers luxury 3 star hotel accommodation in Cahir and is the ideal base for your hotel break in the South East of Ireland. Cahir House Hotel is steeped in history, with the main tourist attraction in Cahir being the Island in River Suir, on which sits a medieval castle, Cahir Castle, once a stronghold of the Butler dynasty, Cahir House replaced Cahir Castle in the 1770s as the ancestral home of the Butlers of Cahir, whose titles include Barons of Cahir and Earls of Glengall. For sixty years Cahir House was home to Lord Cahir’s family until 1853, when Richard, Earl of Glengall was declared bankrupt and the entire estates were sold. However, twenty years later, his daughter, Lady Margaret succeeded in repurchasing Cahir House and the entire Cahir estate and retained ownership until 1961 when her son Richard Butler Charteris died, thus ending a 600 year association between the Butlers and Cahir. In 1927, Miss Nora Burke leased the premises and open Cahir House Hotel, for over forty years, the reputation of the hotel as a family run, warm, welcoming and hospitable establishment spread far and wide. Indeed, the visitor’s books include such names as Eamon De Velara, W.T Cosgrave, Mae West, Douglas Fairbanks, Walt Disney, Jackie Kennedy to name but a few. Cahir House Hotel is still a family run hotel, of which we are very proud, the legacy of genuine warmth and accommodation continues to incorporate the ideals and integrity of a time gone by with a modern efficiency and professionalism. Situated centrally in Cahir, Co. Tipperary, Cork, Waterford & Shannon Airport, Cities such as Kilkenny, Cork, Waterford, Limerick, a mere 1 hour drive away from Cahir House Hotel.

overview:
La Birra Oi è uno dei primi progetti in Italia che prevedono la produzione di birra partendo da materie prime prettamente di origine Italiane.
Il nome Oi deriva dal nome dialettale del fiume Oglio nel cui parco agricolo coltiviamo dal 2013 l’orzo e dal 2015 luppolo dai quali otteniamo questa birra unica.
La Birra Oi non viene filtrata né pastorizzata, questo per preservarne la
purezza e per esaltarne sentori ed aromi. La lenta rifermentazione in bottiglia, poi, ne
evolve il gusto, affinandola nel tempo.
L’importante spuma bianca che si formerà versandola, soffice come una crema, sarà garanzia di genuinità ed aiuterà a mantenere il giusto equilibrio tra aromi e perlage.
Allo sguardo, colpirà il colore ambrato del sole al tramonto; all'olfatto un profumo fragrante di malto tostato; al palato, un gusto fresco ed elegante, con una nota amara perfettamente bilanciata.
Birra Oi:
ispirata alle nostre tradizioni, prodotta con tecnologie evolute, dedicata agli amanti del
‘buon gusto’ italiano.
specialites: Produzione e commercializzazione di Birra Oi

overview:
At Global Titanium, we believe quality is a product that we deliver with every pound of titanium we sell.
Whether you are ordering 1,000 pounds or 100,000 pounds, our focus and commitment remains the same.
This commitment is what makes Global Titanium a company you can depend on every time. Global Titanium is an integrated manufacturer of titanium metallurgical products. Located in Detroit, Michigan, USA, Global Titanium processes all types of titanium scraps; melts, analyzes and processes ferrotitanium; screens and segregates titanium sponge; and produces titanium HDH powder.

Global Titanium's business consists of utilizing recycled materials to produce titanium metallurgical products for use by the producers of titanium, steel, stainless steel, aluminum and powder metallurgy products.

Recycled materials are purchased from around the world, including all forms of titanium scrap, by-products, co-products, off-grade materials, semi-finished products, and other raw materials.

Global Titanium is an ISO 9001:2008 registered company with a firm commitment to quality and safety in every aspect of the company's business.

overview:
At Wellstone Studio, we believe in serving those who serve others, in their work, in their homes, and in their communities. Our clients are Coloradans who are making (or want to make) a big impact on the world—the ones who take responsibility for the well-being of others. 

The biggest problem for service-minded people? We tend to come last on the list, and being last on our own list can lead to anxiety, burnout, depression, and being overwhelmed. We think that we “should be more”: more organized, more resilient, more optimistic, more patient. Meanwhile, many of us are living with hidden and vicarious trauma—the kind that comes from helping, serving, and leading others.

Integrative art therapy is one of the most effective methods of healing, connection, and recovery. Combined with EMDR and talk therapy, our whole-brain and whole-heart approach will help you get back out into the world you love, free to rediscover and redefine a life that feels much, much lighter.

name: Baffinland
hq: Suite 300, Oakville, Ontario, L6H 0C3, Canada
overview:
At Baffinland, we work and live beyond the Arctic Circle, mining iron ore at our Mary River Property, located in the Qikiqtani Region of Nunavut on Baffin Island; one of the world’s most captivating and seldom seen destinations.
 
We are a unique company with a strong management who have amassed specialty experience on northern mining projects through all phases of Inuit consultation, permitting, construction and operation. Our workforce brings together the modern practice of safe, sustainable mining and the enduring value of a traditional culture, which is rapidly advancing. The result is a work and community experience you won't find anywhere else.
 
We are looking for people ready to share, build, and grow with our company.


About Baffinland:
 
Baffinland is privately owned, 50 % by ArcelorMittal and 50 % by Iron Ore Holdings LP, with ArcelorMittal remaining as the project operator. Baffinland’s Head Office is located in Oakville, Ontario, Canada.

In addition to its Head Office, Baffinland maintains a year-round presence at its exploration camp at the Mary River site, and community liaison offices in Iqaluit, Igloolik, Pond Inlet, Hall Beach, Clyde River, and Arctic Bay. Baffinland’s engineering and environmental teams have a wealth of Arctic development experience.

Schools play a major role in raising and educating our children, but that is not sufficient. The diverse blends of children with different backgrounds can affect your child and lead him to acquire healthy or even corrupted practices. While at school, most of the students don’t have enough time to carry out sports and fitness activities where such activities are deemed essential for proper physical and mental growth. Similarly, parents might get overloaded with their daily burdens allowing less time for their children to play and practice sports and entertaining activities.

Utilizing Emirati vision and global expertise, Junior Gym takes over this mission to offer the UAE a leading fitness center allowing children to discover their talents while shaping their little bodies. Junior Gym is equipped with a vast collection of soft tools, gymnastics equipment and flooring that meet the highest international standards. Our dedicated fitness trainers are backed by international experience which helps to create a safe and trusted environment that strictly adopts related health and safety policies.

Parents may rest assured knowing that their children are in safe hands!

Dari indikator indikator aspek keuangan yang dijadikan standar pengukuran, kinerja Indonesia Ferry mendapatkan total nilai 92,8. Nilai ini bahkan lebih baik dari BUMN BUMN yang selama ini sudah dikenal oleh masyarakat luas memiliki kinerja yang baik.

Predikat Sangat Bagus tersebut menunjukkan bahwa kerja keras seluruh jajaran dewan komisaris, direksi dan karyawan dalam menjalankan program-program perusahaan sudah berada dalam jalur yang tepat. Sejak dua tahun terakhir, Indonesia Ferry telah menjalani tranformasi bisnis menjadi perusahaan pelayaran penyeberangan yang berorientasi pada keselamatan dan keamanan dan pelayanan pengguna jasa. Sebagai contoh pencapaian yang telah dilakukan antara lain modernisasi pelabuhan penyeberangan, penerapan sistem tiket elektronik, peningkatan kualitas dan kuantitas perawatan kapal dan alat alat keselamatan kapal, juga reformasi birokrasi dan pelayanan kepada pengguna jasa.

Riset yang dilakukan oleh Biro Riset Majalah Infobank meneliti 112 BUMN yang layak dirating dari 141 BUMN yang ada saat ini. BUMN yang menjadi obyek riset adalah BUMN yang telah merilis laporan keuangannya selama dua tahun berturut turut. Sebanyak 29 BUMN tidak dirating karena, antara lain, laporan keuangannya masih unaudited, laporan prognosis, laporan berupa RKAP, dan ada yang sudah ditutup namun masih tercatat.

Rating 112 BUMN Infobank ini menggunakan pendekatan aspek keuangan, yaitu tiga tiga indikator pertumbuhan dan tujuh indikator rasio keuangan penting dengan bobot masing-masing seragam. Indikator-indikator tersebut kemudian diberi bobot nilai. Jumlah total nilai indikator indikator yang diperoleh setiap BUMN kemudian di beri kategori sebagai berikut: 81 hingga 100 mendapat predikat Sangat Bagus, nilai 66 hingga kurang dari 81 berpredikat Bagus, 51 hingga kurang dari 66 Cukup Bagus, dan di bawah 51 Tidak Bagus.

 

(Corporate Secretary/Info Bank No.371 Februari 2010)

name: Laser Additive Solutions Ltd
hq: 1A Bankwood Industrial Estate, Bankwood Lane, New Rossington, Doncaster, South Yorkshire, DN4 7EP, United Kingdom
overview:
Laser Additive Solutions (LAS) Ltd provides advanced laser based Additive Manufacturing (AM) services across the whole breadth of engineering sectors ranging from simple job-shop laser cladding tasks through to comprehensive R&D programmes. 

Founded in 2015, the company is based on 10 years of hands-on experience of world-class Laser Metal Deposition (LMD) project work for both real world production applications and high-end R&D projects. Peter Brown, the owner, has invested heavily in the latest LMD technology to provide a highly capable AM solution.

LMD, also known as laser cladding or the Blown Powder process, involves the use of a highly accurate and perfectly controlled laser beam, manipulated by a CNC driven gantry or robotic system, to deposit fully fused metal onto a pre-existing substrate.

The process can be used for life extension purposes where typically an 'overlay' approach is utilised, to prevent corrosion or wear for instance, or to build material efficient 3D near-net shapes.

A wide range of Titanium, Nickel, Cobalt, WC containing and Steel alloys can be deposited, including Ti64, IN718, and Stellite-6. A key advantage of using a laser is that the process inputs the minimal heat required to achieve successful fusion of the powdered material. 

LAS Equipment:

TRUMPF 2kW TruDisk Laser with fully integrated BEO 70 LMD Processing Head

REIS RL80 Gantry Manipulation System

Oerlikon Metco Twin-10-C Powder Feeder with two hoppers for multi-material applications

Mebitec TopLas3D CAD/CAM software suitable for 'conformal' cladding as well as 3D-build repair/OEM tasks

ROMER Absolute 7525SI Portable CMM Arm with Integrated Laser Scanner, for reverse engineering tasks with an accuracy of ±0.063mm 

LAS Services:

LMD Job-Shop Production

LMD R&D

LMD Consultancy

3D Inspection/Scanning Sub-Contract

name: Beloit College
hq: 700 College Street, Beloit, WI, 53511, United States
overview:
Beloit College was founded in 1846, when Wisconsin was still a territory. The early curriculum was built on the classical tradition, but students were given an unusual amount of freedom to choose their own courses. Today, Beloit is recognized for its longstanding commitment to curricular innovation, and its first-year initiatives and international education programs.

The Beloit College community is diverse and noted for its passionate engagement with ideas and the world. Twenty-seven percent of its students are domestic minorities or students from countries other than the United States. No more than ten percent of a graduating class is represented in any one of Beloit's majors.

97% of Beloit's 105 full-time faculty members hold a Ph.D. or the highest degree in their field. Teaching is the faculty's highest priority but all professors are active scholars and artists. Professors serve as mentors, guides, and partners on research projects and academic work. A strong tradition of student-teacher collaboration contributes to the college's lively intellectual community.

Beloit offers more than fifty majors, more than thirty minors, and a number of dual-degree and preprofessional programs. A flexible curriculum, grounded in rigorous study encourages independent research, fieldwork, and collaboration with peers and professors. Coursework is interdisciplinary, experiential, and global in scope. The average class size is 15 students; Beloit has a 12:1 student-to-faculty ratio.

name: Tourismuszukunft
overview:
Die Zukunft des Tourismus gestalten

Mit diesem Anspruch berät und begleitet Tourismuszukunft touristische Unternehmen und Verbände. Basierend auf dem weit gefächerten Know-how unserer Netzwerkpartner unterstützen wir unsere Kunden dabei, neue Strategien und Lösungen fürs digitale Zeitalter zu finden.

Wir denken über die Zukunft nach

und helfen Ihnen, diese für Ihr Unternehmen zu gestalten. Ob Analyse, Beratung, Schulung oder Umsetzung – für jedes Prozess-Stadium finden Sie im Tourismuszukunft-Team kompetente Partner. Unsere Erfahrung und Flexibilität helfen uns, Sie bei höchst unterschiedlichen Anliegen zu unterstützen. Statt auf Einzelprojekte setzen wir auf Prozesse: So begleiten wir viele unserer Kunden schon seit Jahren – und gestalten gemeinsam mit ihnen den Fortschritt. Dieses gemeinschaftliche Vorgehen ist auch der Grund, warum uns Tourismusdestinationen, Reiseveranstalter, Reisemittler, Branchenverbände und Hotels in ganz Europa vertrauen. 

Realizing Progress

Beflügelt von unserer eigenen Neugier, liefern wir schon seit 2006 mit dem Tourismusblog Orientierung und Inspiration zu aktuellen Trends und Themen im eTourismus. Wir sind offen für neue Entwicklungen – und lieben es, kreative Ansätze für Marketing und Vertrieb, für Produktentwicklung und Marktforschung aufzuzeigen.

Ein Ensemble von Enthusiasten

Mit Netzwerkpartnern im gesamten deutschsprachigen Raum agieren wir nahe am Kunden. Durch unser breit aufgestelltes Themenspektrum finden wir individuelle Lösungen für alle strategischen und operativen Anliegen. Denn jeder unserer Netzwerkpartner ist nicht nur ein anerkannter Spezialist, sondern brennt auch leidenschaftlich für die Themen, die er vertritt.

Diese Leidenschaft hat uns zu einem Ensemble Gleichgesinnter geformt, das dieselbe Neugierde, Leichtigkeit und Lebensfreude teilt. Gemeinsam sind wir Tourismuszukunft – das Ensemble von Enthusiasten im Tourismus.

name: Ministeriet for Børn, Ligestilling, Integration og Sociale Forhold
hq: Holmens Kanal 22, Copenhagen, 1060, Denmark
overview:
Ministeriet arbejder for at skabe reelle fremskridt for udsatte borgere i vores samfund. Ministeriet skal sikre, at kommuner og regioner får mere for mindre og mere af det, som virker effektfuldt for borgerne. 
Ministeriets forretningsområde dækker den centrale forvaltning af det sociale servicesystem samt opgaver vedrørende ligestilling, integration og familieret.
Ministeriets koncern består af departementet, Socialstyrelsen og Ankestyrelsen.

Mission
Ministeriet for Børn, Ligestilling, Integration og Social Forhold opgaver er flerstrengede og omfatter både fx juridisk sagsbehandling og praksisundersøgelser i Ankestyrelsen, policy udvikling i departementet og projekt- og implementeringsarbejde i Socialstyrelsen. Med den fælles strategi for ministeriet, giver vi ministeren og Folketinget det bedste grundlag for en virkningsfuld social- og integrationspolitik til gavn for borgerne.

Strategiske mål
Som koncern har vi sat os tre strategiske mål for vores arbejde:
- Altid vidensbaseret: Vores tiltag bygger på bedste viden om, hvad der virker, og hvorfor det virker.
- Optimal ressourceudnyttelse: Vi udnytter de økonomiske ressourcer med størst mulig effekt.
- Intentioner bliver til virkelighed: I samarbejde med centrale aktører sikrer vi, at regler og indsatser implementeres.

overview:
Vcura, de hulp om ouderen lekker gezellig zelfstandig thuis, te laten wonen. In de omgeving waar u controle heeft over wat zich daar afspeelt. 
Dat is een belangrijke bijdrage aan het welzijn en de kwaliteit van leven. 
Indirect betekent dit ook dat de partner en/of de kinderen worden ontlast en zelf meer tijd hebben voor hun eigen dagelijkse beslommeringen, wetende dat hun partner, vader/moeder in goede handen is.

Vcura, verzorgt onder andere:
Met u samen: alleen is maar alleen. Samen zijn en samen doen maakt de dingen een stuk leuker
Groepsactiviteiten: Leuke dingen ondernemen met mensen om u heen, vriendschappen sluiten en nieuwe ontdekkingen doen.
Er op uit: Even wat anders, even weg uit de dagelijkse sleur en genieten van een andere tijdsbesteding. Dit kan zijn een middag of avond lekker een spelletje spelen met anderen, tot een verzorgde vakantie, 
Uiterlijke verzorging: Aandacht voor uw uiterlijk er verzorgd uitzien geeft een goed gevoel en maakt dat u straalt. 
Zorg, hulp en begeleiding: Naast uw persoonlijke (lichamelijke) verzorging is een helpende hand voor andere activiteiten veelal een welkome aanvulling.
Vitaliteit en gezondheid: Vitaliteit van lichaam en geest geeft u energie. Energie die nodig is om uw leven zelfstandig te kunnen blijven leven. Vcura ondersteunt u daarbij met professionele trainers en therapeuten. Ook voor vitamines en mineralen zonder chemicaliën hebben wij een partner. 
Praktische zaken: Vele werkzaamheden die u dagelijks tegenkomt kunnen wel een extra handje gebruiken, of het nu om de woonomgeving gaat of uw administratie.
Handig automatisch: Niet alles hoeft u zelf met de hand te doen. Zeker als het gebruik van uw handen lastiger wordt of als u gewoon van gemak houdt of slechter ter been wordt. Er zijn heel veel mogelijkheden om zaken te vergemakkelijken.
Veiligheid: Uw gevoel over de veiligheid van uw woonomgeving bepaalt voor een belangrijk deel van uw woongenot.

name: Formula Masters China Series
hq: 7F, ONE INDIGO, 20 Jiuxianqiao Road, Beijing, Beijing, 100016, China
overview:
Formula Masters China Series is China and Asia’s leading international junior single-seater championship. It has been specifically designed to provide a platform for the next generation of motorsport stars to develop an essential motorsport foundation which will serve them throughout their racing careers. 

Established in 2013 by Volkswagen Group China’s Sports Car Project China and jointly organized by TopSpeed Limited, the series provides myriad opportunities for fledging talent to hone their skills by creating a level playing field, ensuring talent, rather than financial advantage, dictates success. 

Each race weekend is carefully designed to maximize the drivers’ time in the car, optimizing opportunities to learn and develop. Pre-event testing is followed by a free practice session and two qualifying sessions on the Friday. Races 1 and 2 are held on Saturday, with a third race on Sunday.

The series holds races on the most prestigious circuits in China and across Asia, challenging the drivers to adapt quickly to the various track layouts and testing their racing mettle to the max each and every weekend. 

A major advantage of the FMCS concept is that it serves as an optimum stepping stone to more senior motorsport series within the Volkswagen Group China motorsport family, including: the Audi R8 LMS Cup, the Lamborghini Super Trofeo Asia Series, the Porsche Carrera Cup Asia and the Scirocco R Cup China. From its very first season, many FMCS drivers have stepped up to more advanced series, applying the skills and knowledge learned in FMCS to achieve success there.

Services
Formula Masters China Series offers cost-effective services of the highest standards, all of which are centrally managed, including:
•	Transportation and logistics of cars and spare parts
•	Centrally managed spare parts 
•	Engine technician at each event 
•	Track hospitality at each race 
•	Pit set-up and equipment

name: Südtiroler Bauernbund
hq: K.-M.-Gamper-Str. 5, Bozen, Trentino-Alto Adige/Südtirol, 39100, Italy
overview:
Der Südtiroler Bauernbund (SBB) gehört zu den größten Wirtschaftsverbänden in Südtirol. Als Interessensvertreter und Dienstleister in einem vertritt und berät er über 21.000 Mitgliedsbetriebe.
Ziel ist es, den Bauernstand in wirtschaftlicher, sozialer, kultureller und politischer Hinsicht zu stärken und die Mitglieder gegenüber Behörden, Gewerkschaften und wirtschaftlichen Organisationen zu vertreten.
Die Interessenvertretung auf politischer Ebene erfolgt durch die Entsendung von Vertretern des Bauernbundes in die gesetzgebenden Organe auf Gemeinde-, Bezirks-, Landes-, Staats- und EU-Ebene. Verbandsintern sind der Südtiroler Bauernbund und die bäuerlichen Organisationen flächendeckend auf Orts-, Bezirks- und Landesebene organisiert und eng miteinander vernetzt. 

Neben der Interessensvertretung bietet der Südtiroler Bauernbund zahlreiche Dienstleistungen für seine Mitglieder und teilweise auch für Nichtmitglieder an. Schwerpunkte sind die allgemeine Information der Mitglieder sowie die Beratung und Betreuung in den Bereichen Steuern, Recht, Arbeit und Löhne, Arbeitssicherheit, Förderungen, Betriebswirtschaft, Soziales und Fürsorge, Marketing, Innovation und Erneuerbare Energien und Weiterbildung. 

Der Sitz des Südtiroler Bauernbundes befindet sich in Bozen. Mit einem Bezirkssitz ist der Südtiroler Bauernbund auch in Schlanders, Meran, Bozen, Neumarkt, Brixen, Sterzing und Bruneck vertreten.

name: voetbalvereniging STB
hq: Eikenkamp 5, Hattemerbroek, Gelderland, 8094 PK, Netherlands
overview: In de zomer van 2013 kreeg voetbalvereniging STB een nieuwe impuls en werd er een doorstart gemaakt door middel van verschillende jongens van ‘buitenaf’. Dit heeft geresulteerd in een snelle groei en een professionaliseringsslag van voetbalvereniging STB, maar altijd met het behoud van het gezellige ‘wij-gevoel’ binnen de vereniging.De Boskuip, wat duidelijk zichtbaar is geworden. Ook is de professionaliseringsslag duidelijk op andere gebieden, zoals het goed gebruik maken van social media, een nieuwe website en maatschappij betrokkenheid. In het seizoen 2013/ 2014 heeft STB 1 een goede gooi gedaan naar het kampioenschap in de vierde reserve klasse. Helaas is dit niet gelukt, maar het elftal heeft de uitgesproken ambitie om dit seizoen kampioen te worden, om volgend seizoen een stap hoger te zetten. Tevens is in het seizoen 2014/ 2015 STB 2 opgericht. STB 2 is in de loop van het seizoen een vaste waarde geworden in de zesde reserve klasse. De professionaliseringsslag en de snelle groei van de vereniging is mede gerealiseerd omdat vrijwel elk lid op zijn eigen manier bijdraagt aan de groei van de vereniging. Naast dat de leden sportmannen zijn, zitten ze in verschillende commissies, in het bestuur of helpen mee aan het onderhoud van de accommodatie. Uiteraard hebben alle vrijwilligers een belangrijk aandeel hierin. Er is een nieuwe bestuur gekozen in de vereniging en bekrachtigd door een officiële ledenvergadering. Ernie van Beek is voorzitter, Gerjan Spijkerboer secretaris en Stan Termes penningmeester. Wim Rietberg is bestuurslid voetbalzaken en Yvonne During is verantwoordelijk voor de kantine en de accommodatie. Het bestuur wordt ondersteund door verschillende commissies. Merendeel van de commissies zijn in het afgelopen seizoen opgericht, en de commissies krijgen steeds meer gestalte. Daardoor is er een stabiele organisatie binnen de vereniging opgezet, wat leidt tot de verdere professionalisering van de vereniging.
specialites: Ambitieus, Prestatie, Gezelligheid, Sportief

name: SDEE / Σ.Δ.Ε.Ε. (ΣΥΝΔΕΣΜΟΣ ΔΙΚΗΓΟΡΙΚΩΝ ΕΤΑΙΡΕΙΩΝ ΕΛΛΑΔΟΣ)
overview:
Ο Σ.Δ.Ε.Ε.(Σύνδεσμος Δικηγορικών Εταιρειών Ελλάδος) συστήθηκε ως Σωματείο στις 26 Απριλίου 2010. Σκοπός του είναι η προαγωγή του θεσμού των δικηγορικών εταιρειών και του δικηγορικού λειτουργήματος εν γένει. Δίνει μια δυναμική παρουσία στο νομικό κόσμο και αναδεικνύει μια νέα μορφή άσκησης της δικηγορίας μέσα από τη συλλογικότητα, ανταποκρινόμενη στις ανάγκες της σύγχρονης κοινωνίας και οικονομίας, η οποία λειτουργεί μέσα από σύνθετους θεσμούς και διεθνοποιημένες σχέσεις.

Η δημιουργία νέων θεσμών και η διόγκωση του κανονιστικού πλαισίου απαιτεί αφ’ ενός εξειδίκευση και αφ’ ετέρου συντονισμό νομικών υπηρεσιών μέσω της αντιμετώπισης των σύγχρονων απαιτήσεων με συλλογική δράση. Οι δικηγορικές εταιρείες μπορούν να καλύψουν τις ανάγκες αυτές και να καθοδηγήσουν τους πελάτες τους στο σωστό σχεδιασμό των σχέσεών τους και στην αποτελεσματική επίλυση των θεμάτων που γεννώνται από τη δραστηριότητά τους.

H Δικηγορική Εταιρεία αποτελεί φυτώριο ανελίξεως νέων νομικών παρέχοντας το κατάλληλο περιβάλλον ώστε να εξελίξουν τη γνώση τους και να αναπτύξουν την πρωτοβουλία τους στηριζόμενοι στην πείρα, την καθοδήγηση και την ωριμότητα του οργανισμού της.

overview:
Iowa farmer Arthur Luscombe founded Art’s Way Manufacturing in 1956, to produce and sell a PTO powered grinder mixer he developed on his farm near Dolliver, Iowa. His first product was a great success that marked the beginning of his amazing career as an inventor and entrepreneur. In 1959, Luscombe moved the company from his original plant in downtown Armstrong to its present location, and the grinder mixer line was expanded to include OEM work for companies such as Massey Ferguson, Owatonna and Case or as it was known then, International Harvester.

Today, Art’s Way has approximately 200 employees and operates its 4 business units in 7 facilities. Arthur Luscombe’s dedication to innovation, quality and durability remains the central focus of our products and business practices. We take pride in the quality of our grinder mixers, sugar beet harvesters, graders, plows and other farm machinery, and continue to expand our product lines to meet the needs of our customers.

name: RPMG Research
overview:
Our Mission: 
RPMG Research Corporation is committed to serve business and government agencies through data collection, detailed analyses, and dissemination of information about current trends and practices in the business-to-business use of bank commercial card, e-procurement, and other payment technologies affecting the procure-to-pay and order-to-cash cycles of organizations.

Our Specialty:
RPMG Research Corporation specializes in market research that provides insight into our understanding of evolving procurement practices, in particular as they relate to and are supported by bank commercial card technology. Since inception in 2000, our projects include numerous major market studies in the use of bank purchasing card, corporate travel card, and electronic accounts payable in North America. One key objective of our benchmark survey series is to provide card issuers and card-using organizations with information that will help them maximize the value they receive from using or accepting commercial cards. To ensure that card issuers and their customers obtain the maximum benefit from the information, RPMG continues to assist card users and card issuers in many ways, including: customized analysis and performance reports for card-using organizations, customized analysis of survey data for targeted use and issues, training sessions with account representatives to ensure maximum dispersal of information, and seminars/speaking sessions to communicate commercial card market dynamics.

Supporters of RPMG Research:
RPMG Research personnel have conducted presentations or special studies and analyses of data for organizations including Mastercard, Visa, The National Association of Purchasing Card Professionals, The National Institute of Government Purchasing, The Accounts Payable Network.
