name: Residentie Molenwijck
overview:
Residentie Molenwijck biedt senioren comfortabel, zelfstandig en zorgeloos wonen in een stijlvolle ambiance op vijfsterrenniveau nabij de Efteling en de Loonse en Drunense Duinen. De leefomgeving straalt vitaliteit, een warme sfeer en aandacht uit. 

Exclusief
Het zijn vooral de kleine dingen die het doen. De huurders genieten in hun appartement in alle privacy van het wonen en leven in een unieke omgeving. De vijfsterrenservice verrijkt het dagelijks leven. Nieuwe bewoners en hun gasten zijn vaak verwonderd over de bijzondere sfeer en service die zij ervaren binnen Residentie Molenwijck. Zij voelen zich hierdoor snel thuis. Een excellent team van enthousiaste medewerkers verleent met een brede glimlach de passie en service die u mag verwachten. 

Bourgondisch
Elke dag bereiden de chef-kok en zijn team een diner van de beste verse ingrediënten voor haar bewoners en hun gasten. De bourgondische diners zijn altijd weer een feest, evenals de vele inspirerende en gezellige bewonersactiviteiten. Bewoners bepalen zelf in welke mate ze deelnemen aan het ‘rijke Molenwijckse’ leven. 

Levenslang
Residentie Molenwijck heeft een betrokken en professioneel 24 uurs zorgteam dat u alle zorg geeft die u nodig heeft, zodat u in uw eigen vertrouwde omgeving kunt blijven wonen, ongeacht de zorg die u nodig heeft. Al bijna 40 jaar een uniek concept in Nederland.

Vitaal
Bij de ontvangst voel je het direct. Dit is een bijzondere en vitale leefomgeving met veel persoonlijke aandacht voor elkaar en een aangename sfeer. De organisatie is financieel gezond en biedt haar diensten aan tegen kostprijs.
specialites: Seniorenhuisvesting, Gastvrijheid, Service en wonen, Exclusief wonen, Bourgondisch

name: Car Sharing Salerno

overview:
Il progetto Car Sharing Salerno è un servizio di mobilità alternativo dedicato al centro città, che consente ai propri associati di usufruire di un autoveicolo nuovo, con il massimo dei comforts e a metano, prenotandolo comodamente in base alle proprie esigenze.

Per innalzare la qualità della vita ci poniamo due obiettivi :

Il primo è quello di favorire la mobilità sostenibile nella nostra città, allineandosi alle politiche di viabilità adottate dal nostro Comune e dalla nostra Provincia, riducendo le auto in sosta poco utilizzate dai residenti e aumentando così posti preziosi per visitatori, turisti e utenza commerciale.

Il secondo è il miglioramento della qualità dell’aria che respiriamo, riducendo le immissioni di gas di scarico, introducendo automobili sempre manutenute e alimentate a metano.

I nostri punti di forza:

EFFICIENZA
E’ un servizio che garantisce un’auto nuova, sempre pulita e con il massimo dei comforts

SMART CITY
Nasce per diminuire le auto di proprietà poco utilizzate nel centro città

ESCLUSIVITÀ
E’ un servizio esclusivo e flessibile che si adatta alle esigenze di ogni nostro associato
specialites: servizi, mobilità, ecologia, sostenibilità, assistenza

-	The platform supports all size of online businesses with warehousing and order fulfillment services through a national-wide network of fulfillment centers operated by country’s leading logistic partners including ViettelPost and Kerry Express…

overview:
Since our foundation in 1979, Flaretec have become the global market leader for the design and manufacture of quality specialist products across a variety of industries including Oil, Gas, Petrochemical, Marine and Power. We forge global business links through delivering cost-sensitive, innovative engineered solutions to meet our clients’ specific needs. In May 2014, Hephaestus Holdings bought and realigned the former Haycock and Hague Pipework Systems into the Flaretec brand. This allows production of process packages and pipework systems to complement our vessel market share.

Flaretec provide a specialist premium service to support our clients from design stage to installation. We will accommodate product manufacture to both in-house and client design and specification whilst easily meeting and exceeding expectations, requirements and standards. name: Glocal University - Saharanpur Uttar Pradesh

overview:
At the Glocal University, we strongly believe in harnessing the power of knowledge by combining learning with extensive application-based study and professional ethics, thus maximizing one’s overall potential and nurturing a winning mentality in each of our students.

We believe in a radical approach towards education with in-depth study and international teaching techniques that encourage a practical application of knowledge along with a code of ethics, hence developing one’s inner self and providing the perfect edge.

Vision

Global canvass, local colours—that is what we, at Glocal, simply believe in. It is the prism that refracts all our endeavours—whether it is our architecture, curriculum design, pedagogy, hostel life, laboratories, café or the library. In short, we simply celebrate the liminal space where the ‘global’ meets the ‘local’. We are traditional, yet we are not. We are modern, yet we are not really so. We understand the hybrid nature of the global workplace and that is why no binaries constrain us. To flourish in the world today, one cannot afford substantive and rigid visions of the good life. One has to appreciate the negotiated nature of the contemporary. That is why we emphasize reflexivity, flexibility, diversity and accommodation as key values. While that is the ethos of critical engagement we aspire to craft, we are equally keen to develop top quality professionals for our customers: the corporate, public sector and the academia.

 

Mission

At the Glocal University, we are committed to producing top-notch professionals who have a zeal for perpetual learning and are capable of performing well in diverse professional and cultural settings. While we provide the students with all the tools required to successfully take on the world, we also endeavour to instil in them a healthy cultural rootedness that combines the best of traditional values with modern and progressive sensibilities.

Efficient

Milieu
Alle producten van WashEco zijn biologisch afbreekbaar. Er is geen sprake van verspilling, wegens geen gebruik van water en/of zeep en andere chemische reinigingsmiddelen. Een directe bijdrage aan minder vervuiling in het grondwater en milieubewuster handelen!

name: Hawk Yachts Ltd.
hq: 2 Eaton Gate, London, London, SW1W 9BJ, United Kingdom
overview:
THE GREAT EXPLORERS

HAWK YACHTS is a new company in yacht design. Decades of experience in numerous industries, experienced captains, expedition leaders, naval architects, engineers, designers, project managers, tourism and hotel specialists, talents in all envolved disciplines teamed up, joined by the vision to develop and build the most versatile yachts ever devoped, however never loosing the focus on beauty.

Its first project is SEA HAWK, a 103m, 6,500gt yacht design with Monaco beauty combined with the sea-worthy capabilities to reach the most remote and inaccessible areas of the world’s oceans. This unique yacht provides the owner with Polar Ice Class 6 classification, capable breaking through 80cm of new ice and a design allowing tropical cruising, giving, for example, access to 2,000nm of Amazon exploration. Sea Hawk gives 12,000nm range with over three months storage capacity.

THE MARKET

There is a great interest at this time in expedition cruising with an increasing number of vessels claiming the ground but the current fleet of the world’s superyachts falls short of the ability for true world-wide exploration and adventure. Many yachts lack the sea-worthy capability to do much more than cruise the Mediterranean and offer the owner the occasional fair weather voyage to the Caribbean. There are converted trawlers, of course, but these lack the port status and comfort of a superyacht; then there are the new trawler designs that lack both port looks and sea-worthiness for true exploration.

THE VISION

The ability to cruise the world in total safety and luxury. We ask the question – Why limit yourself? This vision is at the core of this “ocean-up” build, incorporating over 35 features, allowing safe voyaging in extreme conditions but at the same time never losing focus that this is a superyacht design.
specialites: Yacht Development, Explorer Yachts

name: H&H Translations
overview:
H&H Translations to firma zajmująca się zapewnianiem tłumaczeń zarówno ustnych jak i pisemnych. Naszym głównym celem przy pozyskiwaniu klienta jest nawiązanie z nim obopólnej ufności, jako że bez tego czynnika współpraca nigdy nie będzie owocna. Utrzymujemy z klientami ciągły kontakt, aby przekaz informacji był płynny i czytelny; najcięższe i najważniejsze zadania omawiamy twarzą
w twarz dla 100-procentowego zrozumienia.

W H&H stawiamy na jakość, rzetelność i profesjonalizm. Nie odsyłamy klientowi zlecenia, z którego sami nie jesteśmy zadowoleni (a wymagania mamy duże); pracujemy nad nim tak długo aż osiągniemy oczekiwany rezultat. Robiąc to, zawsze pamiętamy o dotrzymywaniu terminu, ponieważ to kolejny kluczowy aspekt udanej współpracy. Jeśli klient jest zadowolony, my również.

Oferta
Tłumaczenia tekstów – specjalizujemy się w tekstach specjalistycznych, a tematyką obejmujemy: cyberbezpieczeństwo, IT, biznes, ekonomia, lokalizacja gier, branża filmowa i inne. Zapewniamy tłumaczenia między językami: polski, angielski, francuski, szwedzki i hiszpański.
Tłumaczenia konferencyjne – oferujemy tłumaczenia konsekutywne, a w przyszłości również symultaniczne.
Zapewniamy korekty, proofreading i poprawki edytorskie.
Reprezentowanie firm wśród zagranicznych kontrahentów – wiemy, że przekaz informacji między firmami o różnych narodowościach musi być jasny i zrozumiały, dlatego oferujemy lingwistyczne pośrednictwo dla firm, które nie czują się pewnie w rozmowach w obcym języku.

name: Digo Bikas Institute (DBI)
overview:
Digo Bikas Institute (DBI) is a research and advocacy organization committed to promote ecological sustainability and social equity at policy and community level. Based in Kathmandu, DBI believes that Nepal (and the rest of the world) can develop meaningfully by identifying and applying alternative ways of meeting human needs without harming the nature and fellow human beings.



Vision
Digo Bikas Institute envisions an ecologically sound, socially just and prosperous society, and that it will continue to be so for future generations.

Mission
Digo Bikas Institute’s mission is to undertake research and action to stimulate informed discussion and strategic thought to advance alternative and local solutions to global problems.

Our Approach
Digo Bikas Institute carries out research, training and advocacy on all aspects of sustainable development. Our research work aims to build evidence for bringing positive policy change. We empower and engage critical mass of informed citizens through our education and trainings. We conduct advocacy work based on the evidence generated through our research and analysis by involving the informed citizens.

We use different approaches to achieve our vision and mission those include research and analysis, seminars and conferences, education and training programs, correspondence and fact finding missions, public consultations and legal interventions, network building and international solidarity, joint campaigns and media.

name: High Pressure Processes Group - UVa
overview:
The High Pressure Processes Group of the University of Valladolid is involved with research and development of processes for industrial application using the principles of efficiency and sustainability as its philosophy. The thermodynamic characteristics of supercritical fluids together with the implementation of process intensification technologies have provided a unique platform for the development of novel processes with applications including:

•	Energy generation from biomass residues. 
•	Waste conversion and upgrading as part of a circular economy philosophy.
•	Formulation and functionalization of high value-added products and nanomaterials from different biomass sources. 
•	New materials development: catalyst supports and hydrides

The expertise of the group in the field of green technologies involves the application of supercritical fluids, microwave heating and ultrasounds together with phenomenological and numerical processes simulation for the development of new processes concepts. This broad expertise has been materialized into more than 160 scientific contributions and long term industrial partnerships for process development and transference of technology.

name: Sussex Business Resource Center
overview:
Living in Sussex County is a great privilege and experience. The beautifully scenic county offers its residents many great outdoor activities including golfing, skiing, hiking and biking. Sussex County is also home to many wonderful farms that provide various harvest-time, family-friendly events. Additionally, the county is home to many, many wonderful restaurants, shops and various other local businesses. However, living in Sussex County can be challenging from a work/commuting perspective as local job opportunities are somewhat limited and this often forces many Sussex County residents to endure long work commutes. To help address this challenge for our county's residents, we started the Sussex Business Resource Center, which will serve as a professional workplace setting from which people can work remotely. The Sussex Business Resource Center will also serve as a place where professionals can gather to collaborate and provide their services to local businesses. The mission of the Sussex Business Resource Center is to help grow our local businesses, which will result in more substantiated growth within Sussex County.

We are a community of people who choose to work together, more productively, to make our work, our lives, our cities and communities better.

SBRC’s community is the intersection of designers, developers, writers, artists, entrepreneurs, scientists, educators, small business owners, telecommuters, marketers, videographers, game developers, and more.

overview:
Bilgi kirliliğinin ve dezenformasyonun yaygın olduğu bir çağda yaşadığımızdan kuşku yok. Beşer tarihinde insanlık bu gün olduğu kadar bir bilgi kirliliği yaşamadı. Bu denli bir bilgi kaosuna maruz kalmadı. Dezenformasyonun ve bilgi kirliliğinin bu kadar yoğun yaşandığı bir çağda insanın bilgilenme sürecini sağlıklı bir şekilde yürütebilmesi için doğru bir yol takip etmesi gerekiyor. Abur-cubur beslenmek beden sağlığı açısından ne kadar sorunluysa abur-cubur okumak da zihin ve kalp sağlığı açısınan o derece sorunlu. Dahası müslümanlar olarak bizim akidemizin şekillenmesiyle doğrudan alakadar olduğu için bilgilenme yolundaki işaret taşlarının tesbiti çok önemli. İşaret taşları yanlış yerleri gösterdiğinde hem dünyadaki modern seküler labirentlerin arasında yolumuzu kaybedebilir, hem de ahiretimiz güme gidebilir.

Sözgelimi insanları kitleler halinde katleden kimyasal ya da biyolojik kitle imha silahları da esasen bir bilgilenme sürecinin ürünüdür. Modern insan kirlenmiş zihniyle elde ettiği bilgiyi insanı, tabiatı ve tüm canlıları tahrip eden, ekolojik dengenin canına okuyan, insanlığın üzerine kanser püskürten bir silaha ya da teknolojiye dönüştürebiliyor. Öte yandan “modern müslüman” da okumayı/bilgilenmeyi insanların akidelerini ve ahiretlerini tarumar eden bir araca çevirebiliyor. Üstelik böyle üretilen bir bilgiyle mikro-kosmosu şekillenen bireyler sömürülmeye ve zihinleri işgal edilmeye elverişli bir kıvama gelebiliyor.

Böyle bir ortamda bilgilenme yolundaki kilometre taşlarının ehemmiyeti tartışılmaz. Rıhle Kitap, yayınladığı ve tavsiye ettiği neşriyatla doğru yönü gösteren kilometre taşları, yoldaki işaretleri tayin etmeyi hedefliyor.

Gayret bizden, muvaffakiyet Allah Teâlâ’dandır.

name: Domaines Comte de Malet Roquefort
hq: Champs du Rivallon, Saint-Emilion, 33330, France
overview:
Aujourd’hui les Domaines de Malet-Roquefort comptent trois vignobles regroupent tous des vins d’exceptions. A côté du Château la Gaffelière, présent à St Emilion depuis 3 siècles, nous trouvons depuis 1999, le Château d’Armens. Anciennement Château Bonnet d'Armens, ce vignoble est situé dans le petit village de Saint-Pey d'Armens, à deux pas de Saint-Emilion. C'est au moment de sa retraite que M. Bonnet a fait confiance à Alexandre de Malet Roquefort, dont la vie a toujours été rythmée par des travaux viticoles au sein des autres propriétés de la famille. Dès lors, le nouveau propriétaire a engagé de lourds investissements pour moderniser les techniques de vinification. Alexandre a eu un véritable coup de cœur pour le Château Armens, ce nouveau Grand Cru dont il veut révéler la personnalité.
Puis en 2001, Aliénor et Alexandre de Malet-Roquefort, tombent sous le charme d’une propriété nommée le Château Chapelle Maracan et située à Mouliets-et-Villemartin, à côté de Saint-Emilion.
Au-delà de la richesse du terroir, c’est le caractère atypique du lieu qui a séduit le couple. En effet, au cœur du vignoble, surplombant les pieds de vigne, se dresse une vieille chapelle qui semble protéger son terroir comme une mère veille sur son enfant.
Ce coup de cœur pour le Château Chapelle Maracan a donné naissance à une grande cuvée \

Printmax er stolte av å jobbe i en bærekraftig industri. Vi jobber proaktivt med våre kunder og partnere for å sørge for kvalitet og tilfredshet i alle ledd.
 
Besøk også vår søsterside som leverer alt av profiltøy, arbeidstøy og sportstøy. www.promomax.no.

זה למעלה מ-5 שנים, בית העסק עץ המחלף מתמחה במכירת ובאספקת עץ ומוצרים נלווים ללקוחות פרטיים, לחובבי עשה זאת בעצמך, לקבלנים, לענף התעשייה ולאנשי מקצוע בכל חלקי הארץ.

העסק מפעיל מחסן עצים גדול ורחב ידיים באזור השרון, בסמוך לכביש 6 ליד קיבוץ חורשים. במחסן העץ מלאי ענק של עץ איכותי מכל הסוגים בשלל גוונים: עץ אורן, עץ גושני, עץ מודבק, עץ איפאה, עץ מחוטא ועוד, עם אפשרות לחיתוך לפי מידה. המגוון הרחב מאפשר לכל לקוח למצוא את המוצרים הדרושים לו, לכל מטרה שהיא: בניית פרגולות, התקנת דקים, בניית מחסן וכו'. במקום תוכלו ליהנות גם מייעוץ מקצועי לבחירת המוצר הדרוש לכם.

העץ המשווק על ידי עץ המחלף נשמר בתנאים קפדניים ומצטיין באיכותו, ומבטיח לכם חומר גלם מעולה, עמיד ואמין.

פרט לאספקת עץ, תוכלו למצוא בעץ המחלף גם ציוד פרזול מכל הסוגים, ציוד טכני וצבעים לעץ – כל הדרוש לכם עבור עבודות עץ, ובמחירים אטרקטיביים.

overview:
We have earned our reputation as being leaders in minimally invasive spinal surgery and have been at the forefront of modernizing spinal surgery operations while remaining highly conservative in our clinical judgment and determination of who is a candidate for surgery.

 CONCIERGE SPINE SURGERY™

 What does it mean to be a “concierge-style surgical practice?” In short, it means that our practice is with you from the beginning to the end of your treatment – for anything and everything.

 Our office assists in travel arrangements and hotel accommodations while you recover in South Florida. Our office always puts patients first! We have experience making your stay, as well as your loved ones' stay, as pleasant as possible and will tailor your visit to your requests or special needs.

 Our staff arranges everything for our patients during the pre-operative process and post-operative process. All appointments including MRIs, medical clearance, and other appointments are all arranged by our office.

 Our staff is extremely caring, professional, and diligent. They take great pride in making this important difference for patients to make sure that the treatment process not only goes smoothly, but is done efficiently and in a timely fashion.

 We employ a team approach method with other physicians to make sure that all surgical/medical matters are treated in the best interest of our patients.

 We also make sure to incorporate conversations with family members throughout the process, so that no patient's family members, loved ones, or friends are ever “left in the dark.” They know they can call my office or me for regular updates throughout the operative period. We strive to eliminate any amount of worry or concern that may develop.

name: Office World AG
hq: Switzerland
overview:
Office World ist der grösste Anbieter von Bürobedarf im Schweizer Markt – für Privatkunden sowie den anspruchsvollen Geschäftskunden.

 Die Geschichte von Office World begann 1988 mit einem englisch-schweizerischen Gedankenaustausch. Zwei Geschäftsleute waren über den Kanal gereist, um die Globus Gruppe als Investor für ihre Geschäftsidee zu gewinnen. Dies gelang ihnen so überzeugend, dass die Konzernspitze beschloss, deren Firmenrechte gleich komplett zu erwerben und den Sprung auf den britischen Markt zu wagen. Schon 1989 war es soweit – Office World war als Teil der Globus Gruppe professionell aufgestellt und eröffnete in England seine erste Filiale.

Bestätigt von den dortigen Erfolgen, wurde das Konzept 1991 auch in der Schweiz umgesetzt. Der ersten Filiale in Pratteln folgten bis heute weitere 23 Filialen und 4 City-Shops. Nach der Übernahme der Globus Gruppe durch Migros ist Office World inzwischen ein selbständiges Unternehmen – mit Migros als Muttergesellschaft. Ein Meilenstein in der Unternehmensgeschichte war die Eröffnung des Internet-Shops. 1998 ging das Sortiment online und machte Office World damit zum einzig wahren Multi-Channel-Anbieter in der Schweiz. Durch die im Frühjahr 2012 eingeführte Mobile-App von Office World wurde die Multichannel-Strategie weiterhin bestärkt und die Zahl der Vertriebskanäle wuchs neben dem Online Shop, den Verkäufen in den Filialen und dem Customer Service Center auf 4. Damit hebt sich Office World von der Konkurrenz nicht nur deutlich ab sondern gibt seinen Kunden die Möglichkeit auf allen möglichen Wegen ihre Bedürfnisse abzudecken. Mittlerweile halten ca. 280 Mitarbeiter über 8.500 Produkte und viele Services bereit.

overview: Seit Oktober 2009 bietet Studentconsulting qualitativ hochwertige und dennoch bezahlbare Finanz- und Rechtsberatung für Privatpersonen und Firmen, insbesondere KMU an. Die Idee zur Gründung der Studentconsulting GmbH ist entstanden, als sich ein Team motivierter Studenten der Universität Zürich dazu entschieden hat, ihr Wissen und ihre Fähigkeiten Privatpersonen und Unternehmungen zur Verfügung zu stellen, für welche die stattlichen Beratungshonorare grösserer Firmen wenig attraktiv sind. name: Dr. Cell Phone LCD Recycling
overview:
Do you have gadgets that are gathering dust somewhere in your home? Are they just taking up space you could otherwise be using?
 
Why don’t you bring those gadgets to Dr. Cell Phone? We will take them off your hands and pay you handsomely for the LCDs we can get from them. With our LCD Recycle services, you can make money while you contribute to humanity’s responsibility to take care of the earth. And when you get home, you’ll realize you didn’t only recycle and make money, you actually gave your home more living space!
 
Are you aware that a rotting LCD produces a chemical that is one of the worst amongst greenhouse gases? A chemical known as Nitrogen Trifuoride (NF3) is released to the atmosphere when an LCD decomposes. Experts have dubbed this chemical the missing greenhouse gas and it’s 17 thousand more harmful to the atmosphere than CO2.
 
So act now! It’s time to gather up all your unused gadgets and send them over to Dr. Cell Phone. Let’s not allow the NF3s to escape! Save the Earth with us and you can make money out of it! Call us for more details!

name: Noor Kids
overview:
In the challenging environment for Muslims in North America, Noor Kids seeks to inspire 4- to 8-year-old children to become strong and confident American Muslims. We produce a colorful, high-quality, activity book series designed to instill Islamic values in an engaging and exciting way.

Through a design thinking approach informed by educational research and new theories about how children learn, we have identified a unique 3-part philosophy to guide our product development. First, we value critical thinking. We stimulate children to use reason to internalize Islam. Instead of focusing on the ‘what’ and ‘how’ of faith, we focus on the ‘why.’ Second, we encourage parent-child engagement. We create content, such as discussion questions and interactive activities, to spark in-depth conversation between parents and children about faith. And third, we affirm the importance of role models. Our four characters – Amin, Shireen, Asad, and Amira – role model successful integration for children, while also making Islamic education relevant for 4- to 8-year-old children.

Our Harvard-sponsored children's books have entered into over 25,000 homes across 25 countries. And, we have been featured on media such as NPR, BBC, Christian Science Monitor, Boston Herald, Business Insider, Bustle, Quartz, MPR News, and dozens of independent blogs.

We've developed a product that parents and children love. Check out our website and visit us on Facebook to learn more.

We have a big problem to solve. We're excited to be part of the solution.

overview:
The U.S. Advisory Commission on Public Diplomacy is charged with appraising U.S. Government activities intended to understand, inform, and influence foreign publics. It is also charged with increasing support for and understanding of public diplomacy. The Commission conducts studies, inquiries, and meetings, and assembles and disseminates information, white papers, reports, and other publications, to the President, the Secretary of State, the Congress, and the public.

The Advisory Commission was informally established in 1946 as the Advisory Committee on Radio Programming. It was formally established as the Advisory Commission on Information in 1948 by the United States Information
and Educational Exchange Act of 1948, commonly known as the Smith-Mundt Act. In 1977, it merged with the Advisory Commission on Educational and Cultural Affairs and was renamed the Advisory Commission on Public Diplomacy.

name: Fred Meyer
overview: The Kroger Co., together with its subsidiaries, operates as a food retailer in the United States. The company operates three formats of supermarkets: combination food and drug stores (combo stores), multi department stores, and price impact warehouse stores or marketplace stores. The combo stores operate as food stores; and provide pharmacies, food and organic sections, general merchandise, and pet centers, as well as perishables, such as seafood and organic produce. The multi department stores offer general merchandise items, such as apparel, home fashion and furnishings, electronics, automotive, toys, and fine jewelry. The combo and multi department stores also have fuel centers. The price impact warehouse stores offer grocery, health, and beauty care items, such as meat, dairy, baked goods, and fresh produce. The Kroger Co. also manufactures and processes food for sale in its supermarkets. In addition, the company operates convenience stores, which offer an assortment of staple food items and general merchandise, as well as gasoline; and fine jewelry stores. As of August 29, 2007, it operated approximately 2,500 supermarkets and multi-department stores in 31 states; and approximately 750 convenience stores and 650 supermarket fuel centers. The Kroger Co. was founded in 1883 and is based in Cincinnati, Ohio.less

name: Street Food Festival
overview:
Street Food Festival Aarhus d. 12. - 22. maj 2016

- Mad fra hele verden - 

Spis dig igennem mad fra hele verden på 40+ forskellige boder, når Street Food Festival skaber rammerne for en både kulturel og kulinarisk oplevelse d. 12. – 22. maj 2016!

Festivallen afholdes på Officerspladsen i Aarhus Midtby, mellem AROS og Ridehuset, kun 5 minutters gang fra Banegården.
Sæt tænderne i den gode stemning og oplev nye, spændende retter i højeste kvalitet i selskab med vennerne, kæresten, børnene eller kollegerne – på Street Food Festival Aarhus er der plads til alle!

Festivallen er en nøje sammensat blanding af talentfulde gadekokke, farverige food trucks, restaurationer og et hav af nye spændende initiativer – fælles for alle er kærligheden for madkunstens mange farver.

Udover smagfulde anretninger i alle former og størrelser, vil festivallen løbende indeholde underholdende indslag for børn, unge og voksne.

Udvalgte dage vil der være mulighed for at deltage i workshops, hvor fx børnene, i samarbejde med en professionel kok, kan komme med i køkkenet og prøve kræft med madlavningen på en sjov og lærerig måde.

Torsdag, fredag og lørdag holder festivalpladsen åbent til midnat, hvor unge og ældre kan nyde en aften med musik, stand-up, og events

overview:
AWI Steel is a medium sized fabrication company based in Silverwater, Sydney NSW. Specialising in fabrication and installation of structural steel and miscellaneous metal work on infrastructure projects across NSW.
AWI Steel has been in business for over 23 years. We have grown from a small company with a couple of employees to a medium size company that now has 20 employees. We have an excellent relationship with our staff and this is shown by staff being employed with us for up to 23 years. Over the years with have moved with times and technology. This includes machinery and software to increase or work capacity.
At AWI Steel our Work Health, Safety policy is based on a belief that the wellbeing of people employed on site, or people affected by our work, is a major priority and must be considered during all work performed on our behalf. We contribute the success of our Health and Safety Management Plan to pro-active planning of all work activities with due consideration given to implement WH&S controls that are suitable to each given situation. 
AWI Steel prides itself on being reliable, cost effective. We are a team of professionals who provide the highest quality in service and products to our clients.
AWI Steel is based at 36 Day St North, Silverwater. The premises consist of a factory, upstairs and downstairs offices, car park and storage yard.
Services that AWI Steel offer:
Cost estimations
Shop Drawings (in house, Tekla Structures)
Beam line work (in house)
Fabrication
Delivery (with crane truck)
Installation (2-3 site crews)
Finishes to steel (galvanising or paint)

Projects include;Cronulla Rail Alliance - John Holland, Richmond Rail Alliance - Leighton, Southern Freight Line - Leighton, ETTT Alliance - Leighton. Works including Overhead Wire Structures, Handrails, Structural Steel, Anti-Throw Screens, and Miscellaneous metal work.
